Package com.google.appinventor.client.explorer.commands

Provides abstract and concrete classes for various commands that can be executed through button presses and context menus within the Designer.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddFormCommand
    A command that creates a new form.
    BuildCommand
    Command for building a target in a project.
    ChainableCommand
    Abstract base class for chainable commands that perform some action on a ProjectNode.
    CommandRegistry
    Registry of context menu commands.
    CommandRegistry.Entry
    An entry in the command registry.
    CopyYoungAndroidProjectCommand
    A command that brings up a wizard to copy a Young Android project.
    DeleteFileCommand
    Command for deleting files.
    DownloadFileCommand
    Command for downloading files.
    DownloadProjectOutputCommand
    Command for downloading a project target

    This command is often chained with SaveAllEditorsCommand and BuildCommand.
    EnsurePhoneConnectedCommand
    Command for testing if the phone is connected
    GenerateYailCommand
    Command for generating the Yail code for the current project and saving it to the server.
    MiniProgressBar
    A widget that displays progress on an arbitrary scale.
    MiniProgressBar.TextFormatter
    A formatter used to format the text displayed in the progress bar widget.
    ProjectNodeCommand
    Class for UI commands that can be added to the context menu of a ProjectNode.
    SaveAllEditorsCommand
    Command for saving all editors.
    ShowBarcodeCommand
    Command for displaying a barcode for the target of a project.
    ShowProgressBarCommand
    Command for displaying a barcode for the target of a project.
    WaitForBuildResultCommand
    Command to wait for the result of a build
